data.description: Hard to find in this price range, Ralston split-entry home just needs some fine tuning. Features include vinyl windows, durable steel siding, Newer roof, Newer Furnace and AC, a sprinkler system, and a practical "Tuff Shed" for additional storage. The double garage is roomy. Inside, the bedrooms boast original hardwood floors, while the main bath features a ceramic floor. The basement hosts a comfortable family room with carpeting and a convenient 3/4 bath. With fantastic street appeal and a spacious fully fenced backyard, this home is a delightful find.
